	]b
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"Have to land the crystals on the boxes. Like Tetris, you can speed up their descent by holding down. Down is held for the entire run except for a portion where the angle is too extreme on one of the crystals, where down is let go for the exact number of frames it takes for the crystal to adequately land on the box.
	$LF
]div
