[div class=p 
	[b 
		"Magic Rainbow Potion
	]b
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"This is the hardest game in the set and technically should be last, but the menu routing put it here best. You have to link all the columns with at least one flow of magic liquid. This was a nightmare to even figure out RTA. Once I figured out the combination, I went back and optimized the path to be the best possible in terms of movement.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	[b 
		"Twin Dragon Match
	]b
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"It's a guessing game and a match game. There is some skill required for a TAS, as I opt to activate the card next to the previous last activation of the set, to ensure quickest pickings. I created a route that allows no cards to be more than a space away until the final card.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	[b 
		"Pegasus Flight School
	]b
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"Mostly battling against bad movement. I figured out you can clip into the clouds if you do the flying trick, which also causes you to immediately land and be able to jump again. I also discovered the first glitch in this game which is that if you hold left or right on a certain frame after jumping, you can shoot straight up, however this was not used as the vertical gains were too high and caused a late landing.
	$LF
]div
